    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__Parse_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase]

    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__Parse_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

) AS [t]

    SELECT [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t].[Stock], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[Id] = @__Parse_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-18 01:39:55.512 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (27ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-18 01:50:54.924 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

2024-04-18 02:02:20.057 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM [Products] AS [p]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-18 14:07:27.051 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-18 23:33:44.388 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (36ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'

2024-04-20 11:54:31.467 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-20 12:50:19.888 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-20 22:43:03.224 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (2ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-20 23:02:42.748 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (3ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [Products] AS [p]
2024-04-20 23:08:05.236 +04:00 [INF] Executing OkObjectResult, writing value of type 'ECommerceAPI.Application.Features.Queries.Product.GetAllProduct.GetAllProductQueryResponse'.
2024-04-20 23:08:05.239 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]

        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-20 23:54:00.675 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

2024-04-21 01:43:53.773 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

2024-04-21 12:23:34.809 +04:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (1ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Name], [t].[Stock], [t].[Price], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[Discriminator], [t0].[FileName], [t0].[Path], [t0].[Storage], [t0].[Showcase], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]
FROM (
    SELECT [p].[Id], [p].[Name], [p].[Stock], [p].[Price], [p].[CreatedDate], [p].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreatedDate], [t1].[Discriminator], [t1].[FileName], [t1].[Path], [t1].[Storage], [t1].[Showcase], [p0].[ProductImageFilesId], [p0].[ProductsId]
    FROM [ProductProductImageFile] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [f].[Id], [f].[CreatedDate], [f].[Discriminator], [f].[FileName], [f].[Path], [f].[Storage], [f].[Showcase]
        FROM [Files] AS [f]
        WHERE [f].[Discriminator] = N'ProductImageFile'
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[ProductImageFilesId] = [t1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductsId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[ProductImageFilesId], [t0].[ProductsId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[AppUserId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id], [t0].[BasketId], [t0].[CreatedDate], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Quantity], [t0].[UpdatedDate], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreatedDate0], [t0].[Name], [t0].[Price], [t0].[Stock], [t0].[UpdatedDate0]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Id], [b].[AppUserId], [b].[CreatedDate], [b].[UpdatedDate]
    FROM [Basket] AS [b]
    WHERE [b].[Id] = @__basket_Id_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [b0].[Id], [b0].[BasketId], [b0].[CreatedDate], [b0].[ProductId], [b0].[Quantity], [b0].[UpdatedDate], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [p].[Name], [p].[Price], [p].[Stock], [p].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0]
    FROM [BasketItems] AS [b0]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [b0].[ProductId] = [p].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[BasketId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id]
